{"tid":1505602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"End Game - 香港國際機場","createTime":"2019-08-25T14:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:55:31.000Z","uid":61886,"like":79,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"5a12ebe62dbba7c35596c2bf0a7e6efd5ba0916f","tid":1505602,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"地區戰場已經好難打得贏<br />\n每次都損兵折將<br />\n係時候將戰場轉移去機場<br />\n<br />\n每個星期六日全力入機場<br />\n唔好再呃自己係去做文宣<br />\n入機場只有一個目的<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n每星期目標癱瘓兩日<br />\n<br />\n去到10月1日都未有回應五大訴求<br />\n只好再進一步行動<br />\n<br />\n和理非手足<br />\n用盡一切方法搭車入去<br />\n務求塞爆所有陸路交通<br />\n有隊就排 入唔到機場都要塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足<br />\n準備定full gear入去<br />\n預備有最差既情況發生<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0a6873c1f57df3dbc1d37b25958d9a537bdcdcb5","tid":1505602,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f5cc6fbcea0386c209297c806300a3ccbbca6265","tid":1505602,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdj38zV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjdj38zV.png&h=468e810e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56f06016c8a8c5bfa9ad72c11f9070aea61ebc03","tid":1505602,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gd3TMno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgd3TMno.jpg&h=2f1a0f9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"444347bf61ca22355a9c907b1096c049d3e84a2a","tid":1505602